Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:08.48,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I wrote a game \Nwas back in fourth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:13.70,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,The creator has fun making the game, \Nand the player laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:18.97,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely enamored with \Nthat simple, happy communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:24.25,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I was a serious \Nfreeware game developer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.38,sign_582_5_Nobe_s_Game_Room,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nobe's Game Room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.38,sign_582_6_Home_________Abo,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Home             About            Projects            Forum            Contact
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.38,sign_582_7_Freeware_games_b,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Freeware games by Nobe! \NPlease download and enjoy. \NI appreciate feedback on the forums.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:31.51,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,But if you ask me if making games \Nwas always fun, the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.28,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,I started it as a hobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.39,Italics Dialogue,Kelp,0000,0000,0000,,but with the chronic pain of creation,
